NAME
sws_reload_config - Request the swocserver daemon to reload it's config file.
SYNOPSIS
#include <libswocserver.h>

int sws_reload_config();
DESCRIPTION
The sws_reload_config function reads the swoc.conf configuration file and
requests the swocserver daemon to reload it's configuration file.
RETURN VALUE
0 on success.
.br
mge_errno on failure.
ERRORS
On failure mge_errno will be set as required.
